text: And if there is no such thing, the entire US system of government is doomed.

I was just telling a friend that...man, it gets your heart going. I keep thinking, WTH DID THEY THINK WAS GOING TO HAPPEN WHEN THEY GOT IN? Did they think they were just going to sit in there and run the Country? Did they think Trump was going to start actually giving a shit about anyone but himself? How can people be so damn gullible, so damn pathetically victimized by life to think OUR WHOLE GOVERNMENT was in on a stolen election? Don't you think ONE REPUBLICAN would have stood up as a whistle-blower on that criminality by Democrats? I keep thinking Putin or someone has found out how to brainwash or turn these people into Zombies via the Internet! I still have a hard time believing people can honestly be this STUPID!
